{"tid":1635753,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[解決方案] 熱門已被「標題黨」「引戰黨」攻陷","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:06:34.000Z","uid":190579,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"594c1393fae9ef0e55cf176295d195823cabd1e1","tid":1635753,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"問題大家都知唔使講，我只講<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解決方案</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n連登改咗新規距<br />\n大家既習慣都要變<br />\n善用全新「推」和「拉」</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱門準則之「推」</span></span></strong><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">單一用戶 (Unique User) 的<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>觀看次數</strong></span>及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停留時間</span></strong>。</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n因為你哋入到緊要post，花半秒回個「推」，就一世都唔返入去<br />\n要個post keep住浮，係要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同一個人</span></strong>不斷入番個post <br />\n所以大家唔好淨係推，要入去<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>留低一齊討論</strong></span>，集思廣益。睇埋下面留言，睇下樓主係唔係標題黨同fake news撚<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱門準則之「拉」</span></span> </strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>不推文回覆數量：例如在一個主題中如有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大量會員使用不推文回覆</span></strong>，將會大幅減低熱門分數。</ins></span><br />\n因為有人討論廢post 時唔用不推文。<br />\n如果你想佢沉，唔係要留低同佢罵戰，咁樣會推咗post <span style=\"font-size: small;\">(睇番上面)</span><br />\n亦都唔係要離開個post，應該要入去<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用不推文，回個「拉」</strong></span>，再快快頭也不回走人，唔再入番個post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[公告] LIHKG 常見問題公告 2019-09-25<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n大家幫手<br />\n用正確既方法<br />\n將此post 推上熱門</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"040ea24ef59013bbd7c71fded4b750f93eaf0e05","tid":1635753,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e2d825c1b024ddbf92e2918f5d50658ae41d60","tid":1635753,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d815184cd616f4036deee15fc269eea1a3a91f","tid":1635753,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051d12f66adde7e46ba4037514b4f21017517c4e","tid":1635753,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c39a75a2d1f934d79ba1dd22cf392051a1c292a9","tid":1635753,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前真係無留意 p仔幫推"},{"pid":"8ded78ab9b7bd33cde018709fcf42e93e32c6e54","tid":1635753,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39a75a2d1f934d79ba1dd22cf392051a1c292a9","tid":1635753,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前真係無留意 p仔幫推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"你好似推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"b3a95aefcdcdf06fc6d6e5747e85c8f013358d3d","tid":1635753,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97a9051a8f3ece0e2f404bf4227eef1cf07e72aa","tid":1635